      "content": {
        "text": "Welcome to Advanced Language Skills! In this lesson, you'll explore five innovative ways to deepen your understanding of language. You'll learn to transform the emotional tone of sentences, discover how idioms connect across different languages, build visual maps of word relationships, match sentence rhythms and stress patterns, and identify tricky false friends between languages. These skills will help you become a more nuanced and effective communicator!"
